</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C33D1CE3FFA6FF8DFF05FBE36B951876" pageId="4" pageNumber="22" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8B984F68FFA6FF8DFF05FBE36BA01BE7" blockId="4.[150,1438,324,1896]" box="[198,1270,1135,1162]" pageId="4" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis id="B953937AFFA6FF8DFF05FBE36E1B1BE4" bold="true" box="[198,333,1135,1161]" pageId="4" pageNumber="22">Etymology</emphasis>
:—The epithet refers to the villous pubescence, very characteristic in this taxon.
</paragraph>
