<emphasis id="B953937AFFA6FF8DFDD0F8A46D37182C" box="[531,609,1832,1857]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="22">villosa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB63299FFA6FF8DFDAAF8A46C0C182F" author="Glaziou, A. F. M." box="[617,858,1832,1858]" pageId="4" pageNumber="22" refId="ref4384" refString="Glaziou, A. F. M. (1913) Plantae Brasiliae centralis a Glazious lectae. Memoires of the Societe Botanique de France 3 g." type="journal volume" year="1913">Glaziou (1913: 632)</bibRefCitation>
